title: FANTOM Update: Add fUSDT market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list fUSDT on FANTOM C.R.E.A.M. market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: Update and improve FANTOM market.

For:
 Add fUSDT market with Collateral Factor: 75% and Collateral Cap: $3M
Against: 
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
